BEGIN_TEXT
\{ textbook_ref_exact("Rogawski ET 2e", "16.2","21") \}
$PAR 
Compute the line integral of the vector field \(\mathbf{F}=\left< $a y,-$a x\right> \) over the circle \(x^2+y^2=$r2\) oriented clockwise

$PAR
\(\int_{$curve} $FF \cdot \,d\mathbf{\,s}  =\) \{ans_rule()\}
$PAR

END_TEXT 
